Halucigen drops in after Cygnar.
"No, another bot won't confuse him.....I will confuse him, hahahaha"
He looks at Ignatius and begins to try and make him hallucinate that he 
was trapped by wires to wall, unable to move and with more than a 
hundred bot's guns trained on him.
